### Test Statistics Endpoints
### Base URL
@baseUrl = http://localhost:4000/api/v1

### 1. Get Region Statistics (30 days)
GET {{baseUrl}}/statistics/region?regionCode=3273&period=30d
Content-Type: application/json

### 2. Get Region Statistics (90 days)
GET {{baseUrl}}/statistics/region?regionCode=3273&period=90d
Content-Type: application/json

### 3. Get Region Statistics (1 year)
GET {{baseUrl}}/statistics/region?regionCode=3273&period=365d
Content-Type: application/json

### 4. Get Leaderboard (Top 10 Regions This Month)
GET {{baseUrl}}/statistics/leaderboard
Content-Type: application/json

### 5. Get Overall Platform Statistics
GET {{baseUrl}}/statistics/overview
Content-Type: application/json

### 6. Get Trends (Last 30 Days)
GET {{baseUrl}}/statistics/trends?days=30
Content-Type: application/json

### 7. Get Trends for Specific Region (Last 90 Days)
GET {{baseUrl}}/statistics/trends?days=90&regionCode=3273
Content-Type: application/json

### 8. Get Trends (Last 7 Days)
GET {{baseUrl}}/statistics/trends?days=7
Content-Type: application/json

