### Notes:
# - All endpoints are cached for 5 minutes (leaderboard: 10 minutes)
# - Region codes use BPS (Badan Pusat Statistik) codes
# - Leaderboard requires minimum 5 reports per region
# - Resolution rate is percentage with 1 decimal place
# - Satisfaction ratings are 1-5 scale
# - Trends show daily aggregated data

### Common Region Codes (Indonesia):
# 3273 - Kota Bandung
# 3174 - Jakarta Selatan
# 3578 - Surabaya
# 3471 - Yogyakarta
# 3374 - Semarang
